### **Node.js + Express + TypeScript + PostgreSQL + React + React Native**

A full-stack event management and ticketing system with **QR code tickets**, **email notifications**, **role-based access**, **event analytics**, **organizer dashboards**, **attendee mobile app**, and **admin management tools**.

