# ğŸ§© **Overview**

This is a complete event management platform that allows users to:

âœ”ï¸ Discover events
âœ”ï¸ Purchase tickets
âœ”ï¸ Receive QR-coded passes
âœ”ï¸ Scan tickets at the entrance
âœ”ï¸ Get automated event reminders
âœ”ï¸ Manage event sales and analytics
âœ”ï¸ Administer users, events, categories, and permissions

Both **web** and **mobile (React Native)** versions are available.

---

# ğŸš€ **Features**

### ğŸ‘¥ **User Authentication**

* Register & Login (JWT)
* Secure password hashing (bcrypt)
* Forgot password + Email reset link
* Role-based access (Admin, Organizer, Attendee)

### ğŸ« **Event Booking**

* Event creation, update, delete (Organizer)
* Ticket types (Regular, VIP, Early Bird)
* Real-time availability check
* Ticket purchase
* PDF/Email ticket delivery

### ğŸ” **Event Discovery (Public)**

* Search events
* Filter by category/date/location
* Pagination
* Featured events

### ğŸ“§ **Email Notifications**

* Welcome email
* Ticket purchase email (with QR code)
* Organizer ticket sale alert
* 24-hours event reminder

### ğŸ“± **QR Code & Check-In**

* Generate QR codes per ticket
* Scan with mobile app
* Validate & mark attendance

### ğŸ“Š **Analytics**

* Weekly sales summary for organizers
* Event ticket breakdown
* Total revenue
* Check-in statistics

### âš™ï¸ **Admin Panel**

* Manage users
* Manage events
* Manage categories
* Approve event organizers

