# ğŸ—ï¸ **Project Architecture**

```
Backend (Node + Express + TS)
Frontend Web (React + TS)
Mobile App (React Native + Expo)
Database (PostgreSQL)
Email Service (Nodemailer)
QR Code Service (qrcode)
Scheduler (node-cron)
```

